=3D"https://www.technologynetworks.com/tn/articles/the-friedman-test-387454=
#D1"><b></b></a></p><p class=3D"MsoNormal"><b><a href=3D"https://www.techno=
logynetworks.com/tn/articles/the-friedman-test-387454#D2">Friedman test for=
