<div id=3D"D2"><h2><b><span lang=3D"EN-US"><div id=3D"D2">Friedman test for=
mula</div></span></b></h2><p class=3D"MsoNormal"></p></div>




<p class=3D"MsoNormal">To find the test statistic for the Friedman test, Fr=
iedman=E2=80=99s <i>F</i>, we use the following formula:</p>




